data.title: 57 Convenient Nationwide Locations
data.meta_description: WellnessMart: Finally! A convenient and affordable way to see a doctor. With us, there's no hassles, and no hidden fees. Just stop by one of WellnessMart's conveniently located offices, and we'll take care of the rest.
data.text:
Owned and managed by physicians, Wellnessmart excels in clinical practice, efficient workflows, and high touch customer care. We optimize our entire company for the pre-employment requirements of large and small employers. We understand the importance of speed, while adhering to the highest standards of clinical practice and accuracy.

Wellnessmart serves thousands of corporate clients across America and has the highest rated clinics. We offer all conceivable services from TB tests, drug tests, and physicals, to mask fits, CPR testing, background checks and fingerprinting. What sets Wellnessmart apart is our commitment to providing all these services under one roof, making the process simple and convenient for applicants, and ensuring the fastest turnaround times for employers.
